@startuml Secuencia-Motor-Workflow-Ciclo1
title Ciclo 1 - Secuencia: completar actividad y enrutamiento automático
autonumber

actor Funcionario
participant "Angular\n(Mis actividades)" as UI
participant "MyActivitiesController" as MAC
participant "MyActivitiesService" as MAS
participant "FormSubmissionService" as FSS
participant "TramiteService" as TS
participant "WorkflowRoutingService" as WRS
database "MongoDB" as DB

Funcionario -> UI : Completar actividad + formulario
UI -> MAC : PUT /api/my-activities/{id}/complete
MAC -> MAS : completeActivity(...)
MAS -> FSS : validate + save FormSubmission
FSS -> DB : form_submissions
MAS -> TS : advance after completion
TS -> WRS : resolveNextActivities(tramite, responses)
WRS -> DB : workflow_transitions\n+ workflow_activities
WRS --> TS : siguiente(s) actividad(es)
TS -> DB : actualizar Tramite\n+ TramiteTask nuevas
TS -> DB : TraceItem\n(ACTIVIDAD_COMPLETADA, TAREA_ASIGNADA...)
MAS --> UI : OK
UI --> Funcionario : Bandeja actualizada\n(polling 12s)

note over Funcionario, WRS
  El funcionario NO invoca /advance.
  Solo administradores (depuración).
end note

@enduml
